      <section id="id-182350627968">
        <title>PRACTICE</title>
        <para id="id3965087">1. Work in groups of three. Take turns to be A (the waiter or waitress) and B and C (two customers). Write out a menu, or use an available menu (such as the one from Saigon Palace), and imagine that the meal is in progress. Practice these exchanges:</para>
