          <media id="id1171476918002" alt=""><image src="../../media/graphics1-5c7a.png" mime-type="image/png" height="199" width="629"/></media>
        </figure>
        <para id="id3965130">2. Work in groups of three or four. One of you is a waiter/waitress, and the others are customers. Imagine that you are having dinner at Saigon Palace Restaurant. Act out a conversation between the waiter/waitress and the customers during the meal.</para>
