      <title>SECTION 3:READING</title>
      <para id="id3965461">1. Pre-reading</para>
      <para id="id3965466">Discuss the answers to the following questions.</para>
      <list id="id3965474" list-type="enumerated">
        <item>What should a waiter/waitress do when serving customers? What shouldn't he/she do?</item>
        <item>How is he/she supposed to carry plates, glassware and utensils when serving guests?</item>
        <item>What are some rules for service at the guest table?</item>
      </list>
      <para id="id3965497">2. Reading</para>
      <section id="id-404892285977">
        <title>SERVICE RULES</title>
        <para id="id3965504">
          <!--Empty sections are illegal in CNXML 0.5.  This empty paragraph is a place holder that added as a byproduct of the word importer.-->
        </para>
      </section>
